"Click the \"Checkout\" button of the course for which you requested "
"financial assistance"
msgstr "Maddi yardım talebinde bulunduğunuz kursun \"Ödeme\" butonuna tıklayın"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:64
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:17
msgid ""
"Verify that the price of your course has been reduced, then enter your "
"payment information"
msgstr ""
"Kursunuzun fiyatının düşürüldüğünü doğrulayın, ardından ödeme bilgilerinizi "
"girin"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:72
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:19
msgid "After that, you will be able to check out with the discount in place."
msgstr "Bunun ardından, indirim uygulanmış olarak ödeme yapabileceksiniz."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:80
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:21
msgid ""
"Thank you for your participation with edX. We hope you enjoy the course!"
msgstr "edX'e katılımınız için teşekkür ederiz. Kursun keyfini çıkarın!"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:9
#, python-format
msgid ""
"edX offers an 80%% discount to students who qualify for financial "
"assistance. The deadline to apply this discount is"
msgstr ""
"edX, maddi yardıma hak kazanan öğrencilere 80%% indirim sunar. Bu indirimi "
"uygulamak için son tarih"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/subject.txt:3
msgid ""
"Congratulations! Your financial assistance application has been approved"
msgstr "Tebrikler! Maddi yardım başvurunuz onaylandı"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:21
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:4
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in edX. We have reviewed your financial "
"assistance application, and unfortunately, it was not accepted."
msgstr ""
"edX'e ilginiz için teşekkür ederiz. Maddi yardım başvurunuzu inceledik, "
"ancak maalesef kabul edilmedi."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:29
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:6
msgid ""
"We apologize, this course isn't eligible for financial assistance. We "
"encourage you to apply again for another edX course that isn't restricted."
msgstr ""
"Özür dileriz, bu kurs maddi yardım için uygun değil. Kısıtlanmamış başka bir"
" edX kursu için yeniden başvurmanızı teşvik ediyoruz."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:36
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:8
msgid "You can view a list of restricted courses in our Help Center:"
msgstr ""
"Kısıtlanmış kursların listesini Yardım Merkezi'nde görüntüleyebilirsiniz:"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:43
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:10
msgid "We encourage you to keep exploring:"
msgstr "Keşfetmeye devam etmenizi öneririz:"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:4
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in edX. We have reviewed your financial "
"assistance application, and it was not accepted."
msgstr ""
"edX'e ilginiz için teşekkür ederiz. Maddi yardım başvurunuzu inceledik ve "
"kabul edilmedi."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/subject.txt:3
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/subject.txt:3
msgid "Update regarding your financial assistance application"
msgstr "Maddi yardım başvurunuzla ilgili güncelleme"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:13
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:2
#, python-format
msgid "Hello %(user_name)s,"
msgstr "Merhaba %(user_name)s,"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:21
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in edX. We have reviewed your financial "
"assistance application, and unfortunately, it was not accepted. "
msgstr ""
"edX'e ilginiz için teşekkür ederiz. Maddi yardım başvurunuzu inceledik, "
"ancak maalesef kabul edilmedi. "

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:27
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:6
msgid ""
"Financial assistance is limited and may only be awarded up to five times, "
"and you've reached the limit of five."
msgstr ""
"Maddi yardım sınırlıdır ve yalnızca beş kez verilebilir; siz de beş kez "
"başvurma sınırına ulaştınız."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:35
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:8
msgid "You are more than welcome to continue auditing the course."
msgstr "Kursu denetim modunda izlemeye devam edebilirsiniz."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:43
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:10
msgid "Please let us know if you have any additional questions."
msgstr "Lütfen ilave sorularınız varsa bize bildirin."
